# Hub Implementation Guide

## Document Discovery Locations
When working with the hub, documents are discovered from these 7 locations:
1. `projects/<slug>/` - Project folder
2. `docs/discovery/` - MANUS, NICHE-INTEL, PAIN-SIGNALS, JTBD, OPPORTUNITY
3. `docs/validation/` - VALIDATION-PLAN, REDTEAM
4. `docs/product/` - NARRATIVE, INSIGHT, PRD
5. `docs/research/` - PERSONA, COMPETITORS, MARKET
6. `docs/portfolio/` - PORTFOLIO-SCORE files
7. `docs/ideas/<slug>/` - Orchestrator outputs

## Naming Convention
All documents must follow: `<DOC-TYPE>-<project-slug>.md`
Example: `NICHE-INTEL-enterprise-design-system-startups.md`

## Key Helper Functions (src/lib/projects/helpers.ts)
- `parseIdeasFromMarkdown()` - Parses ideas from INITIAL_20_IDEAS.md
- `getAllProjectsWithIdeas()` - Merges real projects with virtual ideas
- `findProjectDocuments()` - Discovers documents across all locations
- `readProjectFromFolder()` - Reads project including portfolio score/verdict

